sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as User/Campaign Moderator
    participant UI
    participant APIGateway as API Gateway
    participant BFF as Campaign BFF
    participant Orch as Idea Submission Orchestrator
    participant Campaign as Campaign Service
    participant CampaignSchema as Campaign Schema PostgreSQL
    participant Idea as Idea Service
    participant IdeaSchema as Idea Schema PostgreSQL
    participant Adapter as Document Adapter
    participant Opentext as DocumentStore
    participant Cache as Caching

    Note over User,Cache: Idea Submission Flow

    %% Step 1: User initiates idea creation
    User->>UI: Navigate to create idea
    UI->>APIGateway: Request campaigns for user
    APIGateway->>BFF: Forward request + JWT
    BFF->>Orch: Get eligible campaigns for user
    
    %% Step 2: Retrieve campaigns user is invited to
    Orch->>Campaign: Fetch user's invited campaigns
    Campaign->>CampaignSchema: Query campaigns by user invitation
    CampaignSchema-->>Campaign: Return campaign list
    Campaign-->>Orch: Campaign data
    Orch-->>BFF: Campaign list
    BFF-->>APIGateway: Campaign list JSON
    APIGateway-->>UI: Campaign list JSON
    UI-->>User: Display available campaigns
    
    %% Step 3: User selects campaign and creates idea
    User->>UI: Select campaign and click "Create Idea"
    UI->>UI: Open idea creation form
    User->>UI: Fill idea details (title, description, etc.)
    
    %% Step 4: Load participants from cache
    UI->>APIGateway: Request participant options
    APIGateway->>BFF: Forward participant request
    BFF->>Cache: Fetch cached participants
    Cache-->>BFF: Return participant list
    BFF-->>APIGateway: Participant list
    APIGateway-->>UI: Participant list
    UI-->>User: Display participants for selection
    
    User->>UI: Select/modify participants
    
    %% Step 5: Document upload
    User->>UI: Upload supporting documents
    UI->>APIGateway: Upload document request
    APIGateway->>BFF: Forward document upload
    BFF->>Adapter: Store document
    Adapter->>Opentext: Upload document to store
    Opentext-->>Adapter: Document ID and metadata
    Adapter-->>BFF: Document reference
    BFF-->>APIGateway: Document upload success
    APIGateway-->>UI: Document uploaded
    UI-->>User: Document upload confirmation
    
    %% Step 6: Submit idea
    User->>UI: Submit idea against Campaign ID
    UI->>APIGateway: POST /ideas {campaignId, ideaDetails, participants, documentRefs}
    APIGateway->>BFF: Forward idea submission
    BFF->>Orch: orchestrateIdeaSubmission(campaignId, ideaData)
    
    %% Step 7: Store idea in database
    Orch->>Idea: Create idea record
    Idea->>IdeaSchema: INSERT idea data (campaign_id, title, description, etc.)
    IdeaSchema-->>Idea: Idea created with ID
    
    Idea->>IdeaSchema: INSERT idea participants
    IdeaSchema-->>Idea: Participants linked
    
    Idea->>IdeaSchema: INSERT idea documents
    IdeaSchema-->>Idea: Documents linked
    
    Idea-->>Orch: Idea created successfully with ideaId
    Orch-->>BFF: Idea submission response
    BFF-->>APIGateway: Success response
    APIGateway-->>UI: Idea created successfully
    UI-->>User: "Idea submitted successfully"
    
    Note over IdeaSchema: All idea data stored in PostgreSQL tables